From Brian V Hughes Subject Re Adding VRAM to Quadra W Stuart Jones writes I want to go from K to M VRAM on my Quadra How many K SIMMS do I need to buy None You need to buy ns k VRAM SIMMs They cost about each from your favorite memory distributor Is the current K soldered on the board or do I need to take out the current VRAM before I add more The k is soldered to the logic board There are SIMM slots for expansion Hades